<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Bridal" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Bridal,</orth> nuptial festival: <cit><quote>such observancy as fits the b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 3.4.150" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. III, 4, 150</bibl></cit>.<lb />Adjectively: <cit><quote>b. bed,</quote> <bibl n="shak. jn 2.491" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 491</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. rom 3.5.202" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. III, 5, 202</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.12" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 12</bibl>. <cit><quote>b. chamber,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 4.1.181" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. IV, 1, 181</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. day,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.2.155" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 2, 155</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. dinner,</quote> <bibl n="shak. shr 3.2.221" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. III, 2, 221</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>b. flowers,</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 4.5.89" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. IV, 5, 89</bibl></cit>.
